---
title: Rachael Ray's Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Carrot Celery Slaw and Mashed Taters
description: You’re a key ingredient in the fight against AIDS. Just ask Rachael Ray, whose grilled buffalo chicken recipe was specially crafted for EAT (RED) SAVE LIVES. Featuring a crisp carrot celery slaw, creamy mashed potatoes, and chicken breasts coated in a sauce that’s positively (RED) hot, it’s got all the elements of a dinner classic done right.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rachael-rays-grilled-buffalo-chicken-2e08f497.jpg
